hives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c934174f-a1b9-4f8c-8b7b-c18b3a9b1746/85.jpg","https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c934174f-a1b9-4f8c-8b7b-c18b3a9b1746/86.jpg","https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c934174f-a1b9-4f8c-8b7b-c18b3a9b1746/87.jpg","https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c934174f-a1b9-4f8c-8b7b-c18b3a9b1746/88.jpg","https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c934174f-a1b9-4f8c-8b7b-c18b3a9b1746/89.jpg","https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c934174f-a1b9-4f8c-8b7b-c18b3a9b1746/90.jpg","https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c934174f-a1b9-4f8c-8b7b-c18b3a9b1746/91.jpg","https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c934174f-a1b9-4f8c-8b7b-c18b3a9b1746/92.jpg","https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c934174f-a1b9-4f8c-8b7b-c18b3a9b1746/93.jpg","https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c934174f-a1b9-4f8c-8b7b-c18b3a9b1746/94.jpg","https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c934174f-a1b9-4f8c-8b7b-c18b3a9b1746/95.jpg"],"article":{"title":"插图","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"最高指示要斗私，批修。画了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人以工为主，也要乘学军事，政治、文化也要搞社会主义教育运动，也要批判套产阶级在有条件的地方，也要从事农副业生产，例如大庆油田那样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在工人阶级内部，没有根本的利害冲突。在无产阶级专政下的工人阶级内部，更源有理由一定要分裂成为势不两立的两大派。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国的无产阶级文化大革命形势大好，不是小好。整个形势比以往任何时候都好。形势大好的重要标志，是人民群众充分发动起来了。从来的群众运动都没有象这次发动得这么广泛，这么深入。我们的体大统帅毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"N"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成化热代W"},{"type":"paragraph","text":""},{"type":"paragraph","text":""},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“工代会”会场大门临毛2店8"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他问预育"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"品天期"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新花A会场全景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争读「中央文革贺电张春桥同志作重要报告"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王洪文同志作工作报告小组讨论购买大会宣传画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目录中央文化革命小粗的贺电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（2）给毛主席的致敬电"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（6）张春桥同志重要讲建设一支高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗的英勇善战的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝气莲勃的工人阶队伍（上海市革命委会领导成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（27）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马天水同志贺）·高举毛泽东思想伟大红旗替将无产阶极文化大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（32）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命进行到底（工作报告）（王洪文）给全市工人革命造反派和革命职工的信（上海工人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（50）革命造反派代表会）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（53）开幕（潘国平）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"·（55）开票（王洪文）奢与工人革命造反派团结在一起，战斗在一起，胜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"·（58）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"利在一起（沪三军代表贺）加强工农联盟，将革命进行到底（上海市贫下中农代表翼）.（63）向工人阶学习，做决心把无产阶极文化大革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进行到底的无产阶革命派（上海市革命红卫兵代表贺）.（66）大办毛泽东思想学习班，实现思想革命化（上海染化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（70）八厂革命委会代表发言）"}],"authors":["《一月风暴》编辑部","《工人造反报》编辑部","上海工人革命造反总司令部"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":12}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":6},"tags":[{"name":"王洪文","type":"人物"},{"name":"张春桥","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革","type":"人物"},{"name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}